Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.89,0:01:15.93,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.65,0:10:25.69,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.62,0:23:09.66,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.18,0:26:12.22,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Epilogue}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.73,0:00:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what you do, nothing will change.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.15,0:00:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You should just quit while you're behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.28,0:00:13.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't get anything out of facing reality,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.03,0:00:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,and there's no way to change it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.04,0:00:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better to just ignore it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.13,0:00:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and believe only what you want to believe in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.75,0:00:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that sound a lot easier?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.55,0:00:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be awesome if everyone's life could be that easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.18,0:00:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing great about the real world, is there? It's just dull and annoying as hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.27,0:00:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No one accepts that's the way things are.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.11,0:00:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just stuck with it because they can't deny it either.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.78,0:00:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who actually succeed in life... They just happen to be born
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.16,0:00:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,with the magic ticket called "talent."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.16,0:00:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you realize that, all you have left in life is despair.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.29,0:01:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The ultimate game over.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.42,0:01:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So wouldn't it be better if that kind of reality was wiped away?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.17,0:01:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's complete bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.31,0:01:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,One day you'll see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.53,0:01:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be faced with the boring reality that boxes you in, no matter where you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.99,0:01:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, we don't need our world anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.20,0:01:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Better to let it be swallowed up and for mankind to turn into Shadows...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.91,0:01:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what all those people who're scared to death really want.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.42,0:01:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's my duty to see that they get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.59,0:01:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your bullshit to yourself!{more like fridge logic amirite}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.34,0:01:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to disappear, then go ahead! But leave us out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.35,0:02:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.27,0:02:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Brats like you are so damn naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.31,0:02:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I get that you're all afraid and gotta act tough to cover it up, but geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.77,0:02:12.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm telling you all this based on my own experience in life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.03,0:02:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.24,0:02:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.24,0:02:23.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell {\i1}is{\i0} that thing?{third impact}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.54,0:02:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon...{2deep4u}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.38,0:02:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon the worlds will merge into one!{cry moar tears}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.51,0:02:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like a huge collection of energy!{massive hunk or hunk of massive?}{2 da moon}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming down fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to be afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.06,0:02:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Once everyone turns into Shadows, they'll still keep on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.82,0:02:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll just be oblivious to all the things around them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.19,0:02:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Yukiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:02:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So how's that different from the way things are now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.99,0:02:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No, this'll make things much easier for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter who you are, your lifespan is about 80 years or so, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.92,0:03:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it'd be easier if we all just became Shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to hold back anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.09,0:03:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No more pretending we don't see things.{something about a cave}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody wants anything like that!{something about plato}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez! I'm going bear-serk over here!{something about an allegory}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.93,0:03:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything Adachi says is just nuts!{>mfw}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.35,0:03:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you remember what it was like when your Shadow came out?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.11,0:03:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It must've been enjoying life far more than you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Those things move on pure instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.61,0:03:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They go wild because you defy them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.21,0:03:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Scared?{at least that didn't last 30 seconds and then end up with shinji crushing kaoru}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.63,0:03:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've always wanted to use this.{or was it kaworu}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.05,0:03:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I joined the police so I could carry a real gun, and I thought it'd be fun, but honestly, that was a wash.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.01,0:04:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone around me was such an idiot.{especially that adachi guy ;D.}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.18,0:04:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys don't know when to quit, do ya?{but yea, asuka's name was romanized differently between the anime and manga}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.64,0:04:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want so badly that you'd put yourselves in harm's way?{some pussy. I'd put myself in harm's way for some pussy}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.40,0:04:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it some innate sense of justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.32,0:04:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you just wanted something to spice up your dull lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you any different from the whack jobs who get off on murder?{durr}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You just loiter around Junes and play guessing games!{lolok}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.34,0:04:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So, how many people out there actually think about what's real, or what's right and wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Next to none, I bet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.89,0:04:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Namatame was the one behind those serial murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.10,0:04:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what's real in everyone's eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.81,0:04:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you managed to catch me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you think would happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.36,0:04:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.90,0:04:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's view would shift...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.03,0:05:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the end, no one actually cares who the real killer is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.16,0:05:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That{\i0} is the truth you've been searching for!{it's like when the eva got stabbed}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That isn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.14,0:05:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on! I just told you everything there is to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.23,0:05:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your stubborn ignorance that makes you kids so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.98,0:05:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough of this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.40,0:05:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't even have the balls to shoot me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.45,0:05:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What?{and yu will be reborn as the one}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.28,0:05:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sick of your bullshit!{then fuse with agent smith}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.79,0:05:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what you say,{and then everyone lived happily ever after}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.83,0:05:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't absolve you of your crimes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.33,0:05:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That{\i0} is the truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.46,0:06:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Your twisted logic is that of an immature, egotistic brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,People can't live alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If you give in and sever your ties to human society,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.22,0:06:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,it will naturally become hard to live in it!{wow, this is like, some deep shit}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.93,0:06:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What would you brats know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.56,0:06:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the brat!{I WANT TO FUCK YOU.}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Living is too painful for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.07,0:06:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,but you don't want to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.86,0:06:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course no one would understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just throwing a tantrum like a kid who can't have his way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.03,0:06:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut the fuck up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Chie!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.46,0:06:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna say it flat out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,"Favored by the world," my ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just a worthless criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.43,0:06:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, shut up, shut up!{shut shut shut the fuck up}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.40,0:07:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.45,0:07:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fucking kill you, just like I killed everyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.08,0:07:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.08,0:07:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.00,0:07:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You {\i1}will{\i0} pay for your crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.13,0:07:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Just looking at you pisses me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.55,0:07:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up and get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.97,0:07:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't even stand on your own unless you deny everything I've said!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.61,0:07:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you get for...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We saw the truth in things we never wanted to see just to get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Go fuck yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.16,0:07:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You naive high school brats don't know anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.63,0:08:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You have no idea what kinda shit I've been through!{man, this guy is fucking lame}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.13,0:08:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not the only one who's suffered.{brotagonist to the rescue}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.76,0:08:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.14,0:08:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.89,0:08:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way I can lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.44,0:08:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Face the music!{lol metahumor}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.97,0:08:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What the?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.02,0:08:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:09:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Our world's gonna disappear soon, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.23,0:09:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't have anywhere to go back to anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.36,0:09:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.20,0:09:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, what a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.82,0:09:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.71,0:09:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,All humans will become Shadows.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.92,0:09:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,And I shall descend upon the united world as the master of order.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're from back then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.02,0:09:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Both this world and yours will soon be enclosed in a fog that never lifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.37,0:09:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:10:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Ameno-sagiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.16,0:10:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,One who rules the fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,One awakened by man's desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.50,0:10:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Do what you will,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.26,0:10:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,but your world's erosion cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.22,0:10:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It is an inevitability.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.82,0:10:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Junes is invading! Nooo!{lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.32,0:11:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that eyeball?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pulling the worlds together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.82,0:11:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, the two worlds are going to collide!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.74,0:11:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.28,0:11:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is what creates the fog!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.04,0:11:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mankind's desires are my desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the one who shepherds humans to their true desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans are the ones who tore down the wall between image and reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That is why I decided to expand this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.35,0:11:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You played your part well, stirring up the will of the masses into madness.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But even that is coming to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Mankind will soon become Shadows,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:12:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and live on in the darkness of the fog,\N oblivious of their reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.78,0:12:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut the hell up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.62,0:12:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is part of the sea of unconsciousness that exists within human hearts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.84,0:12:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It is a hollow forest...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.80,0:12:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,born from bloated desire and false imagery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You're sayin' you're the one who created this nasty-ass world?!{nasty ass-world}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.23,0:12:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I bestowed power onto those who could brave the hollow forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.69,0:12:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It was I who made it possible for you to bring about this destiny.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.19,0:12:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the power to enter the TV?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I care!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.16,0:12:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans choose to see only what they wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.66,0:12:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a world filled with desires...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.13,0:12:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Viewed through a window, from which one sees what one wishes to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.55,0:12:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Midnight Channel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.34,0:13:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's why those who got famous suddenly appeared on the Midnight Channel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.43,0:13:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all in people's minds?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.39,0:13:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's been bothering me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.52,0:13:09.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The Midnight Channel we saw in Namatame's hospital room
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.31,0:13:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,wasn't Namatame's true intentions at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.48,0:13:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It came on because we were all thinking,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,"This person must be the killer. He can't be forgiven."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We may not have seen the exact same thing when we watched it by ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.74,0:13:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The more false images one yearns for,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,the more one stops yearning for reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.79,0:13:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And so the forest grows on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.58,0:13:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That is the expansion of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.50,0:13:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,When did we wish for that crap?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.38,0:13:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,To hell with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.55,0:13:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We kept fighting and fighting like morons to get where we're standing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... That I did not foresee.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The ability to master your own Shadow that emerged to kill you,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.90,0:13:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and use its power...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.07,0:13:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,A new and uncertain facet of mankind...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.78,0:14:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it worthy to put my trust in, or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.99,0:14:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be tested.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.75,0:14:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Now everyone will turn into Shadows,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and the world will begin anew in its true form!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.06,0:14:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let our world come to an end!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.53,0:14:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you defy me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.95,0:14:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What can a single person accomplish?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.16,0:14:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I... am not alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.62,0:14:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Human bonds are unstable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.63,0:15:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They are not worthy of your trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Were humans not the ones who departed from reality of their own volition, craving more false images?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.14,0:15:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.93,0:15:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Reality isn't so bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.23,0:15:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what they taught me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I made it this far...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.65,0:15:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,because they were there with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.07,0:15:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm with them,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.82,0:15:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I can change the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.62,0:15:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We will never give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.21,0:15:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.22,0:15:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu!{gay}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:16:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The power of your Social Links
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}created a miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.55,0:16:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.52,0:16:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu!{My nigga!}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.91,0:16:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.45,0:16:57.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu!{senpai}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.67,0:17:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.03,0:17:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Master, it's showtime!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.45,0:17:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, truly!{senpai}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,One shot, one kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.37,0:17:41.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe in you, Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.79,0:17:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! I'll leave the world in your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.96,0:17:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you, partner!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Persona!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You have proven to me human potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.97,0:19:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Mankind's desires are my desires.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.43,0:19:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,If mankind so wishes, I will return at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.47,0:19:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell, children of the new potential.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.53,0:19:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Get outta here. I'm done for anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.45,0:19:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The Shadows will finish me off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.58,0:19:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You came here to kill me in the first place, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.37,0:19:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No, dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.42,0:19:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Your stupid game's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.96,0:19:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Live and face your punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.59,0:19:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it works in our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.39,0:20:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go home, Adachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.44,0:20:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.24,0:20:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a dream...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:27.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro and his friends beat up the bad guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.37,0:20:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They saved us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.76,0:20:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for real! The fog's really gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.38,0:20:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We really did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been so long since the sky was that blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.56,0:20:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's finally over. {This is the end.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.77,0:20:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.77,0:20:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We did this together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.48,0:20:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What're we doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.53,0:20:56.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ooh, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.99,0:20:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.36,0:20:59.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.86,0:21:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Woohoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.16,0:21:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.16,0:21:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... I think that was a little too hard to get on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.83,0:21:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Which part did you mean for us to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.29,0:21:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The "woohoo" part...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.54,0:21:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't we just do it over?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.75,0:21:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, Chie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Do that weird call again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.01,0:21:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Not if you're gonna call it weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.72,0:21:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh. Fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.26,0:21:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all yours, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.18,0:21:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.35,0:21:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!{meh}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.14,0:21:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Woohoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.21,0:21:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Merry Christmas and congratulations on your recovery, Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.80,0:22:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to thank you all again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.55,0:22:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Adachi confessed to the two murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.81,0:22:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There are still things that are unclear about his story,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.02,0:22:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but he's most likely gonna pay for his crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.86,0:22:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.44,0:22:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anyway, this was one strange case.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.32,0:22:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If what you said about a world inside the TV was true,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.32,0:22:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}then everything might make sense,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.82,0:22:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}though I still don't believe it.{more literally, I'm not buying/believing it}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.33,0:22:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've helped us out so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.87,0:22:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was meant to be the other way around, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.88,0:22:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There isn't much time left until spring,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.67,0:22:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I hope I can do some catching up until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.38,0:22:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Same here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.63,0:22:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm looking forward to that.{"Nice to meet you" would be literal here, but it doesn't make much sense in english, isn't it?}{aye}{yap, that's the one}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.79,0:23:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.21,0:23:19.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's way too soon to cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.29,0:23:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.88,0:23:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro, I don't want you to go away!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.47,0:23:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,When I grow up, I'm going to marry you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.06,0:23:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.11,0:23:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd welcome you with open arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.98,0:23:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But hands off while she's underage!{harem complete}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.07,0:23:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you promise you wouldn't cry?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.45,0:23:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.58,0:23:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll leave your room as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.04,0:23:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're as much a part of this family as Nanako.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.71,0:24:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.55,0:24:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.68,0:24:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going back home, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.72,0:24:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to work bear-y hard to protect that place.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.10,0:24:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds good.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.77,0:24:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like we can never see each other again.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.23,0:24:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give me a call. Anytime.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.82,0:24:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The long holidays are coming up soon in May, so you better come back to visit!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.99,0:24:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already reserved rooms at our inn. Let's have another sleepover!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.62,0:24:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This time, our surprise sneak attack won't fail!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.70,0:24:36.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what happened to going back home?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.66,0:24:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That has nothing to do with this! It's entirely different!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.37,0:24:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Teddie's just unbearable, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.54,0:24:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Get it? Un-bear-able?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.71,0:24:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't changed one bit, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.88,0:24:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, Yukiko... You're kinda overdoing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.26,0:24:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The train will be arriving momentarily.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.18,0:24:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For your safety, please stand behind the white line.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.27,0:24:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}While boarding, please do so promptly.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.60,0:25:00.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you better go, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.56,0:25:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.11,0:25:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,See you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.34,0:26:17.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Velvet Room.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.35,0:26:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You've had quite the eventful journey for someone your age.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.86,0:26:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a crystal of power which you have nurtured through your journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.70,0:26:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,An orb that repels fabrications of all sorts, dispels lies, and shines upon the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.21,0:26:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You have formed bonds with those dear to you as you reached out to the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.55,0:26:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll continue to do so.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.26,0:26:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Now go. You'd best be off.
